      <pubDate>Thu, 28 Nov 2024 13:29:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>津巴布韦农业在干旱后复苏，经济增长迅猛</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-28/zimbabwe-sees-growth-surging-as-farming-rebounds-after-drought</link>
      <description><![CDATA[津巴布韦政府预计，随着该国从厄尔尼诺现象引发的干旱中恢复过来，经济增长明年将强劲反弹。厄尔尼诺现象抑制了农业产量，刺激了进口需求，并挤压了国家财政。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-28/zimbabwe-sees-growth-surging-as-farming-rebounds-after-drought</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 28 Nov 2024 13:14:48 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>德国通胀意外保持稳定，支持欧洲央行降息</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-28/german-inflation-unexpectedly-holds-steady-backing-ecb-cuts</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德国11月份通胀率意外保持不变，支持欧洲央行继续降息的理由。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-28/german-inflation-unexpectedly-holds-steady-backing-ecb-cuts</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 28 Nov 2024 13:09:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>寒冷天气刺激需求，德国风力发电量却下滑</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-28/german-power-prices-jump-as-wind-generation-set-to-plunge</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于气温进一步下降导致家庭需要调高恒温器，德国的风力发电量预计将在周五降至几乎为零。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-28/german-power-prices-jump-as-wind-generation-set-to-plunge</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 28 Nov 2024 11:16:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
